  {
    title: 'Drake',
    description: 'What do I have to say? What do you want to hear?',
    link: 'instagram.com/champagnepapi',
  },
  {
    title: 'Ash Thorp',
    description:
      "I know him for creating very realistic+convincing car renders. He's one of the top VFX artists that inspire me.",
    link: 'www.altcinc.com',
  },
  {
    title: 'Maxime Heckel',
    description:
      "He's a learner. He's a sharer. I follow him for the quality of work and research he puts out.",
    link: 'maximeheckel.com',
  },
  {
    title: 'Sebastian Lague',
    description:
      'His videos are really well put. The time spent in research and development is inspiring. Check out his videos.',
    link: 'youtube.com/@SebastianLague',
  },
  {
    title: 'Bartosz Ciechanowski',
    description: 'In-depth engineering research. Man, I idolize this guy.',
    link: 'ciechanow.ski',
  },
  {
    title: 'Paul Henschel',
    description: `Paul has made tremendous contributions around WebGL/ThreeJS with React.
    He leads pmnd.rs and his efforts have lowered the barrier into WebGL considerably.`,
    link: 'github.com/drcmda',
  },
  {
    title: 'Mr DoNothing',
    description: 'His art style is yummy.',
    link: 'instagram.com/mr.donothing/',
  },
  {
    title: 'aarthificial',
    description:
      'Just like Sebastian, aarthificial also runs a devlog channel and builds cool tools.',
    link: 'youtube.com/@aarthificial',
  },
